On Mon, 10 May 2004, Thomas J. Tarka wrote:

> Question: What to do about a stripped hanger(mustache) bar mount?

BTDT.  Helicoil! (or other insert)

Mexican engines come with helicoils installed from the factory!
Apparently the helicoil helps to spread the load onto the soft case
material better than threads carved directly into the case.

George
